{"pageid":266001,"pagename":"Hallowed hammer","title":"Hallowed hammer","displaytitle":"Hallowed hammer","revid":14254835,"properties":[{"name":"smw-semanticdata-status","value":""},{"name":"page_image_free","value":"Hallowed_hammer_detail.png"},{"name":"description","value":"The hallowed hammer is an item that will never break nails inside the Hallowed Sepulchre (regardless of the plank and nail combination used). It can be purchased from the Mysterious Hallowed Goods shop for 100 hallowed marks. Unlike the other hallowed equipment, the hammer does not need to be equipped in order for its effect to work."}],"content":"<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"rsw-infobox infobox no-parenthesis-style infobox-item\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"20\" class=\"infobox-header\">Hallowed hammer</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"20\" class=\"infobox-padding\"></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"20\" class=\"infobox-image inventory-image infobox-full-width-content\"><a href=\"/w/File:Hallowed_hammer.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Hallowed hammer.png\" src=\"/images/Hallowed_hammer.png?43cf2\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"25\" height=\"26\" data-file-width=\"25\" data-file-height=\"26\" /></a></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"20\" class=\"infobox-padding\"></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"7\">Released</th><td colspan=\"13\"><a href=\"/w/4_June\" title=\"4 June\">4 June</a> <a href=\"/w/2020\" title=\"2020\">2020</a> (<a href=\"/w/Update:Darkmeyer\" title=\"Update:Darkmeyer\">Update</a>)</td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"7\"><a href=\"/w/Members\" title=\"Members\">Members</a></th><td colspan=\"13\">Yes</td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"7\"><a href=\"/w/Quest_items\" title=\"Quest items\">Quest item</a></th><td colspan=\"13\">No</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"20\" class=\"infobox-padding\"></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"20\" class=\"infobox-subheader\">Properties</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"20\" class=\"infobox-padding\"></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"7\"><a href=\"/w/Items#Tradeability\" title=\"Items\">Tradeable</a></th><td colspan=\"13\">No</td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"7\"><a href=\"/w/Worn_Equipment\" title=\"Worn Equipment\">Equipable</a></th><td colspan=\"13\">Yes</td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"7\"><a href=\"/w/Stackable_items\" title=\"Stackable items\">Stackable</a></th><td colspan=\"13\">No</td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"7\"><a href=\"/w/Choose_Option\" title=\"Choose Option\">Options</a></th><td colspan=\"13\">Wield</td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"7\"><a href=\"/w/Destroy\" title=\"Destroy\">Destroy</a></th><td colspan=\"13\">Drop</td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"7\"><a href=\"/w/Examine\" title=\"Examine\">Examine</a></th><td colspan=\"13\">Removes the chance of bending nails within the Hallowed Sepulchre.</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"20\" class=\"infobox-padding\"></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"20\" class=\"infobox-subheader\">Values</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"20\" class=\"infobox-padding\"></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"7\"><a href=\"/w/Value\" title=\"Value\">Value</a></th><td colspan=\"13\">10,000 coins</td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"7\"><a href=\"/w/Alchemy\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Alchemy\">Alchemy</a></th><td colspan=\"13\">Not alchemisable</td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"7\"><a href=\"/w/Weight\" title=\"Weight\">Weight</a></th><td colspan=\"13\">0.02 kg</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"20\" class=\"infobox-padding\"></td></tr><tr class=\"advanced-data\"><th colspan=\"20\" class=\"infobox-subheader\">Advanced data</th></tr><tr class=\"advanced-data\"><td colspan=\"20\" class=\"infobox-padding\"></td></tr><tr class=\"advanced-data\"><th colspan=\"7\">Item ID</th><td colspan=\"13\">24727</td></tr><tr class=\"advanced-data\"><td colspan=\"20\" class=\"infobox-padding\"></td></tr></tbody></table><div class=\"infobox-smw-data\" style=\"display:none\"></div>\n<div class=\"floatleft\"><a href=\"/w/File:Hallowed_hammer_detail.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Hallowed hammer detail.png\" src=\"/images/thumb/Hallowed_hammer_detail.png/120px-Hallowed_hammer_detail.png?e7ffb\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"120\" height=\"124\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/Hallowed_hammer_detail.png/180px-Hallowed_hammer_detail.png?e7ffb 1.5x, /images/thumb/Hallowed_hammer_detail.png/240px-Hallowed_hammer_detail.png?e7ffb 2x\" data-file-width=\"1258\" data-file-height=\"1298\" /></a></div>\n<p>The <b>hallowed hammer</b> is an item that will never break nails inside the <a href=\"/w/Hallowed_Sepulchre\" title=\"Hallowed Sepulchre\">Hallowed Sepulchre</a> (regardless of the plank and nail combination used). It can be purchased from the <a href=\"/w/Mysterious_Hallowed_Goods\" title=\"Mysterious Hallowed Goods\">Mysterious Hallowed Goods</a> shop for 100 <a href=\"/w/Hallowed_mark\" title=\"Hallowed mark\">hallowed marks</a>. Unlike the other hallowed equipment, the hammer does not need to be equipped in order for its effect to work.\n</p><p>The hallowed hammer <b>cannot</b> be used in place of a normal <a href=\"/w/Hammer\" title=\"Hammer\">hammer</a> outside the Hallowed Sepulchre.\n</p><p>The hammer also counts as a Saradomin item for the purposes of recharging your run <a href=\"/w/Energy\" title=\"Energy\">energy</a> at the Magical Obelisks at the end of each floor, as well as in <a href=\"/w/God_Wars_Dungeon\" title=\"God Wars Dungeon\">God Wars Dungeon</a>.\n</p>\n<table class=\"rsw-infobox infobox infobox-bonuses infobox\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"10\" class=\"infobox-subheader\"><a href=\"/w/Equipment_Stats#Attack_bonuses\" title=\"Equipment Stats#Attack bonuses\"><img alt=\"Attack icon.png\" src=\"/images/Attack_icon.png?b4bce\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"25\" height=\"25\" data-file-width=\"25\" data-file-height=\"25\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/w/Equipment_Stats#Attack_bonuses\" title=\"Equipment Stats\">Attack bonuses</a></th><td rowspan=\"19\" class=\"infobox-bonuses-image\" style=\"width:123px\"><a href=\"/w/File:Hallowed_hammer_equipped.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Hallowed hammer equipped.png\" src=\"/images/thumb/Hallowed_hammer_equipped.png/123px-Hallowed_hammer_equipped.png?70e9b\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"123\" height=\"348\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/Hallowed_hammer_equipped.png/185px-Hallowed_hammer_equipped.png?70e9b 1.5x, /images/thumb/Hallowed_hammer_equipped.png/246px-Hallowed_hammer_equipped.png?70e9b 2x\" data-file-width=\"479\" data-file-height=\"1357\" /></a></td><td rowspan=\"19\" class=\"infobox-bonuses-image\" style=\"width:135px\"><a href=\"/w/File:Hallowed_hammer_equipped_female.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Hallowed hammer equipped female.png\" src=\"/images/thumb/Hallowed_hammer_equipped_female.png/135px-Hallowed_hammer_equipped_female.png?a68b0\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"135\" height=\"350\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/Hallowed_hammer_equipped_female.png/202px-Hallowed_hammer_equipped_female.png?a68b0 1.5x, /images/thumb/Hallowed_hammer_equipped_female.png/270px-Hallowed_hammer_equipped_female.png?a68b0 2x\" data-file-width=\"628\" data-file-height=\"1627\" /></a></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"10\" class=\"infobox-padding\"></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-nested\"><a href=\"/w/Stab\" title=\"Stab\"><img alt=\"White dagger.png\" src=\"/images/White_dagger.png?db3e5\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"21\" height=\"31\" data-file-width=\"21\" data-file-height=\"31\" /></a></th><th colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-nested\"><a href=\"/w/Slash\" title=\"Slash\"><img alt=\"White scimitar.png\" src=\"/images/White_scimitar.png?2dc8c\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"27\" height=\"30\" data-file-width=\"27\" data-file-height=\"30\" /></a></th><th colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-nested\"><a href=\"/w/Crush\" title=\"Crush\"><img alt=\"White warhammer.png\" src=\"/images/White_warhammer.png?2ff77\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"22\" height=\"29\" data-file-width=\"22\" data-file-height=\"29\" /></a></th><th colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-nested\"><a href=\"/w/Magic\" title=\"Magic\"><img alt=\"Magic icon.png\" src=\"/images/Magic_icon.png?334cf\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"25\" height=\"23\" data-file-width=\"25\" data-file-height=\"23\" /></a></