re</a></span>.</div>\n<table class=\"wikitable sortable align-center-3 align-center-4 align-center-5 align-center-6 align-center-7\"><tbody><tr><th>Seller</th><th>Location</th><th data-sort-type=\"number\">Number<br />in stock</th><th data-sort-type=\"number\">Restock<br />time</th><th data-sort-type=\"number\">Price<br />sold at</th><th data-sort-type=\"number\">Price<br />bought at</th><th>Members?</th></tr><tr><td><a href=\"/w/Mysterious_Hallowed_Goods\" title=\"Mysterious Hallowed Goods\">Mysterious Hallowed Goods</a></td><td><a href=\"/w/Hallowed_Sepulchre\" title=\"Hallowed Sepulchre\">Hallowed Sepulchre</a> lobby</td><td data-sort-value=\"100\">100</td><td data-sort-value=\"1\">0.6s</td><td data-sort-value=\"100\"><a href=\"/w/Hallowed_mark\" title=\"Hallowed mark\"><img alt=\"Hallowed mark 25.png\" src=\"/images/Hallowed_mark_25.png?7ecd8\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"27\" height=\"21\" data-file-width=\"27\" data-file-height=\"21\" /></a> 100</td><td data-sort-value=\"0\">N/A</td><td><a href=\"/w/Pay-to-play\" title=\"Pay-to-play\"><img alt=\"Member icon.png\" src=\"/images/Member_icon.png?1de0c\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" data-file-width=\"16\" data-file-height=\"16\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Changes\">Changes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/Hallowed_hammer?section=3&amp;veaction=edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Edit section: Changes\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\"> | </span><a href=\"/w/Hallowed_hammer?action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: Changes\">edit source</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<table class=\"wikitable mw-collapsible sortable\" style=\"max-width:800px\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th>Date\n</th>\n<th>Changes\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"/w/2_July\" title=\"2 July\">2&#160;July</a>&#160;<a href=\"/w/2020\" title=\"2020\">2020</a><br />(<a href=\"/w/Update:Poll_71_and_Death_Feedback_Changes\" title=\"Update:Poll 71 and Death Feedback Changes\">update</a>)\n</td>\n<td>\n<ul><li>The hallowed hammer is now labeled as a member's item.</li>\n<li>The examine text on the hallowed hammer has been slightly changed; previously, the examine text was \"Removes the chance of bending nails in the Hallowed Sepulchre.\"</li></ul>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"/w/25_June\" title=\"25 June\">25&#160;June</a>&#160;<a href=\"/w/2020\" title=\"2020\">2020</a><br />(<a href=\"/w/Update:Death_Changes\" title=\"Update:Death Changes\">update</a>)\n</td>\n<td>\n<p>The examine text on the hallowed hammer has been changed to reflect its buff from the previous week's update. Previously, the examine text was \"Reduces the chance of bending nails in the Hallowed Sepulchre.\"\n</p>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"/w/18_June\" title=\"18 June\">18&#160;June</a>&#160;<a href=\"/w/2020\" title=\"2020\">2020</a><br />(<a href=\"/w/Update:Poll_71_and_Darkmeyer_Updates\" title=\"Update:Poll 71 and Darkmeyer Updates\">update</a>)\n</td>\n<td>\n<p>The Hallowed hammer now has a 100% chance to not bend nails regardless of the plank and nail combination used.\n</p>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"/w/12_June\" title=\"12 June\">12&#160;June</a>&#160;<a href=\"/w/2020\" title=\"2020\">2020</a><br />(<a href=\"/w/Update:Darkmeyer_Improvements\" title=\"Update:Darkmeyer Improvements\">update</a>)\n</td>\n<td>\n<p>All Hallowed items can no longer be alchemised.\n</p>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Trivia\">Trivia</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/Hallowed_hammer?section=4&amp;veaction=edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Edit section: Trivia\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\"> | </span><a href=\"/w/Hallowed_hammer?action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: Trivia\">edit source</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li>The Hallowed Hammer does not work outside the Sepulchre because making it usable in other areas of RuneScape would require rewriting all hammer-related code across the entire game, a very large and time-consuming endeavour.<sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/Hallowed_hammer?section=5&amp;veaction=edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\"> | </span><a href=\"/w/Hallowed_hammer?action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit source</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small hideQuotes\"><div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Jagex. <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://archive.vn/F3sB3\">Mod Ash's Twitter account</a>. 1 September 2020.  (Archived from <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://mobile.twitter.com/JagexAsh/status/1300821691040497665\">the original</a> on 7 March 2021.) Mod Ash: \"[Would it be possible for the Hallowed Hammer to act like a normal hammer while un-equipped?] It would - but it would require all hammer-related code across the game to be rewritten.\" </span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<table class=\"navbox nowraplinks mw-collapsible\" data-expandtext=\"show\" data-navbox-name=\"Hallowed Sepulchre\" data-collapsetext=\"hide\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" class=\"navbox-title\" id=\"navbox-title\"><div class=\"navbox-title-name-notplain\"><div class=\"navbar\" style=\"float:left;text-